00:58:59.230 --> 00:59:02.250 position:56%
They don't survive, they're made of
cardboard, something like cardboard,

00:59:02.250 --> 00:59:05.960
and there would be 12 Roman
archways, for instance,

00:59:05.960 --> 00:59:09.410
used in one of these entries, and
they're adorned and ornamented

00:59:09.410 --> 00:59:13.760
with all kinds of imagery
representing cardinal virtues,

00:59:13.760 --> 00:59:18.410
biblical and Spanish heroes,
and so on and so forth,

00:59:18.410 --> 00:59:23.370
